nt to be around, and mine had fallen apart previously.)</P><P>If I come back, all of the above will almost definitely lead me to going back to enchanting, even though the thought of practicing JC back up is...painful.  All because the changes sucked away any of the joy that was Hizuka.  He'll still be there for emergencies, but unless things have drastically changed, and by the talks about melee balancing, they haven't, then I'll probaby be going enchanter again.  We play to enjoy ourselves, after all.</P><P>--------------------<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=481" target=_blank>Hizuka</a><BR>Swifttail Master<BR>Initiate of the Celestial Fists<BR>Innoruuk Server<BR>Retired<BR><BR><i>"My Legions of Terror will be trained in basic marksmanship. Any who cannot learn to hit a man-sized target at 10 meters will be used for target practice."</i><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
